JDS - On Quote Details > Materials > Details, made the Quantity group bigger so that Supplier Price List indicator wouldn't overlap with Find Number and Required Ref Designators. [18837-Manager: 7/23/2018 5:44:29 PM]
JDS - Resaved as All Companies [18837-Manager: 7/31/2018 11:36:56 AM]

JDS - adding fields to the interface to show what individual component pricing might look. [18837-Manager: 11/20/2018 2:56:50 PM]
JDS - modifying the Material list via Script Editor [18837-Manager: 11/21/2018 10:20:18 AM]
^ [18837-Manager: 11/28/2018 10:47:22 AM]
JDS - changed a bunch of EpiTextBox to EpiNumericEditor or EpiCurrencyEditor [18837-Manager: 11/28/2018 3:47:44 PM]
JDS - allowed summaries on the grid and summed it. [18837-Manager: 12/3/2018 11:24:21 AM]
JDS - changed the BAQ to work properly. [18837-Manager: 12/6/2018 1:12:29 PM]
JDS - working on making some of the new columns read-only [18837-Manager: 12/6/2018 4:43:35 PM]
JDS - copied Tony's code and made it work when labor amount is changed. [18837-Manager: 12/6/2018 7:42:17 PM]
JDS - That didn't work. Recreated code that sums Install Times and writes to Production Standard when Install Time is changed. [18837-Manager: 12/12/2018 4:07:41 PM]
JDS - adding check box to Summary sheet for "Part Pricing". When this is checked, it will pull the sum of Ext Price into the Line Price on update. [18837-Manager: 12/12/2018 5:20:06 PM]
JDS !!!!!!!!!!!! - started reworking from here !!!!!!!!!! All of the development since 20181214 is being recreated. [18837-Manager: 1/25/2019 3:41:02 PM]
JDS - Rework. changed Qty/Parent to 1 via code
JDS - made changes so that there aren't 3 summary lines in Material Grid [18837-Manager: 1/25/2019 5:01:12 PM]
JDS - added variable for partadd so that when we add a part, the system doesn't have to recalc every field so many times. [18837-Manager: 1/28/2019 3:53:31 PM]
JDS - changed AllowPOTF to false [18837-Manager: 1/29/2019 11:42:03 AM]
JDS - Changed AllowPOTF to true. Improved tab stops on Material Detial. Increased length of some fields to try to fix the right decimal being hidden [18837-Manager: 1/29/2019 12:19:42 PM]
JDS - changed the grid. It was displaying EstMtlUnitCost while the Detial tab was showing EstUnitCost. [18837-Manager: 1/29/2019 12:29:30 PM]
JDS - made changes to partadd so that POTF still calculates when added. [18837-Manager: 1/29/2019 12:59:07 PM]
JDS - tweaking tab stops [18837-Manager: 1/29/2019 2:47:11 PM]
JDS - after Go-Live... made changes to Summary tab so that Status doens't overlap with the WON/LOST indicators. [18837-Manager: 2/6/2019 10:38:31 AM]
JDS - solving why we can't delete an operation after all material has been deleted. [18837-Manager: 2/22/2019 4:47:43 PM]
JDS - added messagebox for when material price is not valid. [18837-Manager: 3/20/2019 11:28:07 AM]
JDS - Making changes to make pricing update when a quote is duplicated and supplier price lists have been changed. [18837-Manager: 2/3/2020 10:38:57 AM]
xs:element.msprop:Description: changes to get pricing to update when dup quote
